String title = "Researchers reveal a useful tip to remember while going for a hike";
String description = "It's always good to bring a slower friend with you on a hike. If you happen to come across bears, the whole group doesn't have to worry. Only the slowest in the group do. And if you turn out to be the slowest, then you can use the elastic band of your underwear to shoot stones on the bear.";
